    <div class="container">
        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <section id="executive-summary">
            <h2 class="section-title">Executive Summary</h2>
            <div class="summary-box">
                <p>
                    <strong>Bond Treasury</strong> and <strong>Atlar</strong> represent the new generation of AI-native treasury management platforms, each targeting distinct market segments with fundamentally different architectural approaches. Both platforms position themselves as complete departures from legacy treasury management systems (TMS), emphasizing AI-native architecture as the core differentiator.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <strong>Bond Treasury</strong> targets large multinational enterprises (S&P 500, NYSE, FTSE-listed companies) with sophisticated treasury operations. The platform emphasizes <strong>autonomous, 24/7 operations</strong> through agentic AI that handles complex dealing, risk management, and cash positioning with minimal human oversight.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <strong>Atlar</strong> targets fast-scaling mid-market and enterprise companies seeking rapid deployment and productivity gains. The platform emphasizes <strong>augmented intelligence</strong>—AI that accelerates human decision-making—with transparent, privacy-preserving workflows and rapid implementation timelines. Atlar has achieved #1 G2 rankings for usability, support quality, and likelihood to recommend.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Company Profiles -->
        <section id="profiles">
            <h2 class="section-title">Company Profiles</h2>
            <div class="profiles-grid">
                <!-- Bond Treasury -->
                <div class="profile-card">
                    <h3>Bond Financial Technologies Ltd</h3>
                    <div class="profile-item">
                        <span class="profile-label">Headquarters:</span>
                        <span class="profile-value">London, UK (+ New York)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-item">
                        <span class="profile-label">CEO:</span>
                        <span class="profile-value">Marcus Strych</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-item">
                        <span class="profile-label">Founded:</span>
                        <span class="profile-value">~2018-2019 (pre-Series A)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-item">
                        <span class="profile-label">Funding:</span>
                        <span class="profile-value">$32M Series A (2020) led by Coatue. Investors include Goldman Sachs, Mastercard, Canaan, B Capital, and John Mack</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-item">
